"### Actions **Spear.** _Melee_ or _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +3 to hit, reach 5 "
"ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 4 (1d6 + 1) piercing damage, or 5 "
"(1d8 + 1) piercing damage if used with two hands to make a melee attack."
msgstr ""

